{"tid":1698533,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"當你習慣死亡 港共已叫成功","createTime":"2019-11-07T14:23:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T16:45:45.000Z","uid":32731,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"730f1bb43cab13f519141d3eee9709e8dca0db9b","tid":1698533,"uid":32731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:23:13.000Z","msg":"係呢一刻所有重大傷亡事件都冇證據指向曱甴<br />\n好快就會淡落黎 又可以分化<br />\n彥霖既案都係呢個下場<br />\n近期最震撼已經係健仔 有哂鏡頭<br />\n但成個香港反應其實冇想像中咁大<br />\n<br />\n一個又一個死去時 因為證實唔到係手足<br />\n就當左做一個&quot;新聞&quot;好快淡忘<br />\n慢慢中共就可以令到香港人<br />\n除左習慣白色恐怖 亦會習慣死亡！<br />\n<br />\n慢慢你既憤怒會下降<br />\n&quot;哦 又死一個 都查唔到嫁啦&quot;<br />\n唔通要公安係你屋企搶屍先識驚？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">就算唔係手足 亦都無可能接受香港變成咁！還原真相緊要 更緊要係唔可以比香港道德淪落</span><br />\n<br />\n由被跳樓跳海開始 到呢家死棄屁係公園<br />\n明顯係試緊大家底線<br />\n唔鼓勵大家浪費太多時間去查<br />\n更應該係要將重點放落 香港人既人性<br />\n麻木左就救唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人唔可以麻木 唔可以習慣</span>"},{"pid":"4540c633476084c9974f382defdfd2390d120fdc","tid":1698533,"uid":32731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:24:40.000Z","msg":"唔可以習慣"},{"pid":"1638be77e2ca6192f774bceba7de33007b075715","tid":1698533,"uid":32731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:25:22.000Z","msg":"唔可以習慣"},{"pid":"09c39b39d6441d175e9e9cdb0dd25ee7824ba293","tid":1698533,"uid":32731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:26:27.000Z","msg":"唔可以麻木"},{"pid":"9df8ac0901aeccf6b66587eba3d69af14758649d","tid":1698533,"uid":76365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:26:27.000Z","msg":"唔可以習慣"},{"pid":"4b11c6e9a51aa0dfcf0663043dace98d7564c368","tid":1698533,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:26:44.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，推post &amp; 借個靚位<br />\n<br />\n******眾籌*******<br />\n鐘庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 (eg. 721, 831) &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 話比全世界聽：5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n(<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌到而家先45%</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 仲要大家支持)<br />\n<br />\n第三&amp;四期民調結果POST <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1</a><br />\n第二期民調結果POST <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌link:  <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqKxyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=c9956a99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a>"},{"pid":"99fe7576881118cc2b8fbbd86f5eeb356ad003ea","tid":1698533,"uid":333360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:26:48.000Z","msg":"無錯, 大家反抗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反抗第一步，建立反擊訊號<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1691213\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1691213</a>"},{"pid":"19e070091feb538c414bfda48bd6dbbed212b3e5","tid":1698533,"uid":76365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:27:11.000Z","msg":"點樣喚醒其他人？"},{"pid":"95be2673c812e6cf0063a58689de205c611c3074","tid":1698533,"uid":176272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:27:16.000Z","msg":"唔可以習慣"},{"pid":"a3628f9d2a1b0062c1c35105347668f95d